{
  "stem": "942.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I sort of crawled on my stomach into the square, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was-- I was facing the gates to the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I could hear some explosions and some heavy equipment moving, and I didn't know what it was because I couldn't see it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, all of a sudden, the camp gate came down, and there was a tank inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I could see a white star on this tank, and I thought this must be an American tank.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were soldiers sitting on the turret of this tank with their guns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'll never forget-- this was-- this will always stay with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember the eyes of these soldiers, they were like saucers, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because what they saw, you know, the-- you know, as they came through, it must have been a terrible sight, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These thousands of dead bodies piled up and the smell, the stink, and-- They saw, those that could walk, they looked like ghosts.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were running towards the tank and they tried to touch the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were scared, the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't want to be touched by these people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember that it was so comical.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They tried to climb higher and higher on this turret, you know, the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was nowhere to climb anymore, but they were just looking down and they were absolutely frightened, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the tanks stopped, because it couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were bodies all over the place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember Jeeps were coming up and these officers were-- or soldiers were getting out of their jeeps, and there was a-- I remember there was somebody, he says, I am a Rabbi.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was really something, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, there's a Rabbi in a uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
